subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution.
Endemic to the southern European Alps. It has been found in the Central Italian Alps: Valtellina, Camonica Valley and Trafoi Valley (
Kulczyński 1915
). The species has also found on the Swiss side of the Monte Rosa Massif (
Schenkel 1927
). The records from Caucaso (
Martynovchenko & Mikhailov 2014
) need confirmation.
